@startuml Sequence_Forgot_Password
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequence {
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #EBF5FB
  ParticipantBorderColor #2980B9
  ArrowColor #2C3E50
  LifeLineBorderColor #BDC3C7
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #ECF0F1
  ActorBackgroundColor #FDEBD0
  ActorBorderColor #E67E22
}
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam NoteBorderColor #F9A825

title Sequence Diagram — Lupa Password & Reset Password

actor "Pengguna" as User
participant "React Frontend" as FE
participant "AuthController" as AC
participant "MailService" as Mail
database "Database" as DB

autonumber

== Lupa Password ==

User -> FE : Klik "Lupa Password"\ndi halaman Login
FE --> User : Tampilkan form\ninput email

User -> FE : Masukkan email\nlalu klik Kirim
FE -> AC : POST /api/forgot-password\n{ email }\n[throttle: 3 req/menit]

AC -> AC : Validasi:\n- required|email\n- exists di tabel users

alt Email tidak terdaftar
  AC --> FE : 422 { message: "Email tidak\n  terdaftar" }
  FE --> User : Tampilkan error
end

AC -> AC : Generate random token\n(60 karakter)

AC -> DB : UPSERT password_reset_tokens\n{ email, token, created_at: now }
DB --> AC : Token tersimpan

AC -> AC : Build reset link:\nhttps://app.com/#/reset-password\n?token={token}&email={email}

AC -> Mail : Mail::to(email)\n.send(ResetPasswordMail\n  (resetLink, userName))

alt Email berhasil dikirim
  Mail --> AC : Email terkirim
  AC -> DB : ActivityLog:\n{ action: "forgot_password",\n  resource: "Auth",\n  details: { email } }
  AC --> FE : 200 { message: "Link reset\n  dikirim ke email Anda" }
  FE --> User : Pesan sukses
else Email gagal (SMTP error)
  AC -> AC : Fallback:\nLog.info(reset link)\n(untuk debugging)
  AC --> FE : 200 { message: "Link reset\n  dikirim ke email Anda" }
  note right: Respons tetap sukses\nuntuk keamanan
  FE --> User : Pesan sukses
end

== Reset Password ==

User -> Mail : Klik link di email
Mail --> FE : Open:\n/#/reset-password?token=XXX&email=YYY

FE --> User : Tampilkan form\nreset password

User -> FE : Isi password baru\n& konfirmasi password
FE -> AC : POST /api/reset-password\n{ email, token,\n  password, password_confirmation }\n[throttle: 3 req/menit]

AC -> AC : Validasi:\n- email exists di users\n- token required\n- password min:8 confirmed

alt Validasi gagal
  AC --> FE : 422 { errors }
  FE --> User : Tampilkan error
end

AC -> DB : SELECT * FROM password_reset_tokens\nWHERE email = ? AND token = ?
DB --> AC : Token record

alt Token tidak valid / tidak ada
  AC --> FE : 400 { message: "Token tidak\n  valid atau kadaluarsa" }
  FE --> User : Tampilkan error
end

AC -> DB : SELECT user WHERE email = ?
DB --> AC : User record

AC -> AC : user.password = new_password\n(Model casts to hashed automatically)

AC -> DB : UPDATE users SET password = hashed\nWHERE email = ?
DB --> AC : Updated

AC -> DB : DELETE FROM password_reset_tokens\nWHERE email = ?
DB --> AC : Token dihapus

AC -> DB : ActivityLog:\n{ action: "reset_password",\n  resource: "Auth" }

AC --> FE : 200 { message: "Kata sandi\n  berhasil diubah" }
FE --> User : Tampilkan sukses\nRedirect ke Login

@enduml
